~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ignore                                    ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ignore <username>

   This command allows you to turn on ignoring on a specific user, 
   ignoring all tells and shouts from that user.  This will not block 
   normal text.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : unignore, showignore, ignall, igntell, ignshout
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
